divs: Sighting Detailsi stepped outside to have a smoke it was shortly after dark. i caught a glimpse of something strange looked up to find something i cannot explain. it was a dark grey boomerang wing shape moving totally silently no visible lights moving from north to south it was directly above my location visible for about a minute it was moving slowly about the speed of a small plane but much larger i estimate it to be about 100 to 200 ft long could not really tell the height at which it was flying . it was such a dark color it was not visible very long as it was dark outside. thought it could have been a flock of high flying birds in a v shape until i google'd what i had seen and found other similar sightings...
Summary: dark grey wing shape moving silently no lights
